Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:02.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林  小林
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.89,0:00:05.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你看我不是究極女僕嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.94,0:00:05.69,Kobayashi S2 - Name,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\pos(955.2,923.8)}托爾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.77,0:00:05.69,Kobayashi S2 - Name,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\fs110\bord8\3c&H9D00EB&\4c&HA51DC4&\pos(1012.8,151)}女          仆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.01,0:00:08.27,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,當然不是  又怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.41,0:00:11.97,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,沒什麼  雖然我也覺得自己已經登峰造極了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.01,0:00:13.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我都說不是了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.51,0:00:15.43,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是我找到了這本書
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.57,0:00:17.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,女僕咖啡廳新開張
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.81,0:00:18.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,還挺近呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.07,0:00:21.87,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這裡寫著「最出色的女僕迎接您的光臨」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.15,0:00:23.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,敢自稱最出色的女僕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.96,0:00:26.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,竟然無視我的存在  進行這種誇大宣傳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.05,0:00:31.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,誇大宣傳可不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.67,0:00:34.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,雖然我眼前的這條龍就在做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:35.18,Kobayashi S2 - Comment Down,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,0)\fs100\bord5\pos(963.2,796.4)}其實是龍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.52,0:00:39.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,總之先用詛咒之炎把她們燒成寸草不生的暗黑塵土
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.43,0:00:41.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,正可謂是又燃又萌？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.43,0:00:41.68,Kobayashi S2 - Comment,,0,0,0,,註：日語中“燃”和“萌”諧音。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.48,0:00:45.90,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不  絕對不準這麼幹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.13,0:00:48.48,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,總之我先去偵察敵情了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.08,0:00:52.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.79,0:00:55.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.58,0:00:56.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.61,0:00:57.41,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.76,0:00:58.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你沒惹什麼事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.08,0:01:00.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我要在那裡工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.99,0:01:01.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.62,0:01:02.95,Kobayashi S2 - HandWrite,,0,0,0,,{\fs90\bord2\pos(790.666,650)}因為我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.96,0:01:06.96,Kobayashi S2 - HandWrite,,0,0,0,,{\fs130\bord2\pos(1103.066,902.133)}小林家的龍女僕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.67,0:02:40.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我當時意志高昂地衝進敵人的伏魔殿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.99,0:02:42.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,還伏魔殿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.70,0:02:43.85,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,打擾啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.66,0:02:46.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你是來面試兼職的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.46,0:02:49.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,穿著女僕裝來的  看來是志在必得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.56,0:02:50.60,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,而且好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.60,0:02:53.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我敗給了你的熱情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.65,0:02:54.44,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,錄取了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.88,0:02:57.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就是這樣  我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.16,0:02:59.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那間女僕咖啡廳沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.36,0:03:02.95,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,反正最近小林和康娜都不在的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.95,0:03:05.12,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我無事可做很閒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.16,0:03:07.50,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你是閒來無事去打工的家庭主婦嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.12,0:03:10.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那你是真要去打工啊  沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.28,0:03:12.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.99,0:03:15.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我可是每天都像這樣做著女僕的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.09,0:03:17.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,已經駕輕就熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.38,0:03:18.55,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不  托爾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.92,0:03:21.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,雖然我現在是在公司上班
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.39,0:03:24.05,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是在老家時是在餐飲店工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.52,0:03:27.09,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,聽好了  不可以小看服務業
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.18,0:03:28.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.47,0:03:32.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,雖然女僕咖啡廳的cosplay女僕形式不符合我的價值觀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.87,0:03:35.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是她們的服務精神值得我尊敬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.44,0:03:37.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這是個好機會  托爾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.13,0:03:40.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你就去學學什麼叫服務業吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.08,0:03:42.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我都有點害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.57,0:03:46.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,從那之後已經有段時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:48.29,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托爾有好好工作嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.95,0:03:50.83,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,小林太愛操心了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.29,0:03:50.83,Kobayashi S2 - Name,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,0)\3c&HB976F6&\pos(962,868.333)}康娜卡姆依
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.29,0:03:50.83,Kobayashi S2 - isDragon,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,0)}（其實是龍）
Comment: 0,0:03:48.29,0:03:50.83,Kobayashi S2 - Comment Down,,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,0)\fs40\3c&HB976F6&\shad10\bord3\4c&H3F4E66&\pos(962.4,1070.866)}（其實是龍）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:52.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,就是這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.96,0:03:55.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:03:57.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,以及大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.12,0:04:01.47,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好多和托爾大人一樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.76,0:04:04.89,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,看來是間很樸實的女僕咖啡廳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.89,0:04:09.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,雖然現在已經不怎麼講萌這種詞了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.84,0:04:12.27,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但這裡還保留了那個時代的遺風
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.89,0:04:13.73,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,看看菜單是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.98,0:04:16.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,還是挺忠實還原基礎的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.82,0:04:18.90,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,每樣菜式有對應的服務
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.11,0:04:22.45,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,大概像「變好吃吧  萌萌心動」這類的咒語
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.45,0:04:23.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,也會各有不同吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:25.11,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林好懂哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.57,0:04:27.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這件事我只告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.26,0:04:31.33,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我以前有想過來這種店裡打工
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.68,0:04:34.54,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,結果失敗了  失敗了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:37.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,雖然我不是很懂  但是同情你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.29,0:04:38.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,比起這些  托爾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:39.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.51,0:04:48.97,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,10號桌的料理做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.07,0:04:49.64,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:51.98,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,盤子不夠了  快補上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.05,0:04:52.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,馬上就好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:04.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好厲害的手法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.95,0:05:06.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不愧是廚師長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.16,0:05:07.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,幫大忙了  廚師長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.99,0:05:09.18,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托爾廚師長大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:10.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不不不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:12.91,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,都是多虧了大家工作效率這麼高
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.91,0:05:15.87,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.23,0:05:17.54,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你是來看我的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.64,0:05:18.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這不是做得挺好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.29,0:05:20.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,讓我吃了一驚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.46,0:05:22.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小事一樁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.86,0:05:24.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,對我而言就是這麼簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.47,0:05:27.18,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這樣的話在女僕之路上就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:28.80,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,女僕…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.93,0:05:32.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這根本不是女僕的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.64,0:05:34.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是廚師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.65,0:05:36.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我去拜託看看能不能換去大堂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.93,0:05:39.36,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不  我覺得這裡很適合你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.73,0:05:41.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,火山龍才適合這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.61,0:05:45.07,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你重新進一次店吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:47.95,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,變好喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.62,0:05:49.45,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:52.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,歡迎光臨  小林
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:54.29,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,嘖  該叫主人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:57.04,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,廚師長當時換來大堂的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:06:00.14,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,說是不想稱呼小林以外的人為主人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.53,0:06:03.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不對  她也從來沒有叫過我主人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:05.80,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,請在這邊坐下稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:08.09,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好  終於可以點單了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.47,0:06:11.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,蛋包飯  蛋包飯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:13.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好  兩份蛋包飯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.93,0:06:15.98,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.27,0:06:20.23,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那就讓我來施展讓蛋包飯變好吃的魔法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:21.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,可愛一點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.08,0:06:22.69,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.72,0:06:25.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,獻予統治世界的影之王
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.77,0:06:29.07,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,以外法將此成就至高
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:30.74,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,祈願豐收
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:31.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,禮讚富足
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.45,0:06:33.28,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,改換價值
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.28,0:06:35.25,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,獻出石碑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:38.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,吾之魔將化作泥沼播撒汙穢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:41.29,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,吾之理將侵蝕理性使人癲狂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:43.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真實虛幻  交織變換
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:50.34,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,變好吃吧  萌萌心動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.61,0:06:56.47,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,來吧  已經變好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:57.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,請品嘗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.25,0:07:00.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這不是魔法是詛咒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:01.51,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.51,0:07:02.91,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,把廚師長給我叫過來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.94,0:07:03.73,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.30,0:07:09.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,廚師長  女僕  龍  都是我托爾
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.74,0:07:16.41,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,至少能力還是有的  僅限能力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.96,0:07:20.25,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但我還是不想當小林以外的人的女僕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:21.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我要辭職
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:23.25,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.17,0:07:25.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你不能走哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.55,0:07:29.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,廚師長做的料理已經是我們店的招牌了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.44,0:07:32.51,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,網上也已經有很多相關的評論
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:34.47,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,廚師長
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.31,0:07:37.64,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那個  既然這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.12,0:07:40.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我就教你們讓料理變好吃的魔法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.19,0:07:41.85,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.23,0:07:45.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,人類施法的話  要先畫出魔法陣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.61,0:07:51.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,歡迎回來  主人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:53.95,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真是間好店呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.33,0:07:56.02,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那麼我要兩份蛋包飯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:07:57.54,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.96,0:08:00.33,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那我要施展變好吃的魔法了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.82,0:08:04.04,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,獻予統治世界的影之王
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.75,0:08:08.80,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這間女僕咖啡廳還真是別具一格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:07.00,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,以外法將此成就至高
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:08.84,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,祈願豐收
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:23.48,Kaboyoshi S2 - Webpage,,0,0,0,,{\frz9.504\fs100\b1\pos(946,780)}蛋包飯很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.48,0:08:24.02,Kaboyoshi S2 - Webpage,,0,0,0,,{\pos(846,780)\frz348.3}料理很美味
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:24.56,Kaboyoshi S2 - Webpage,,0,0,0,,{\fs150\pos(956,838)}蛋包飯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.77,0:08:26.11,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不是料理啊  女僕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.36,0:08:28.23,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,對我作為女僕的評價呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.62,0:08:31.15,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,別弄壞鼠標哦
Comment: 0,0:08:34.41,0:08:36.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,/第1話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.57,0:08:36.99,Kamisama S2 - Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)\blur10\bord1.5\pos(971.467,594.467)}新來的龍、伊露露！（再次請多關照）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.07,0:08:41.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,可以預見接下來的天氣會急劇變化
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.25,0:08:43.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,請隨時關注後續的天氣預報
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.87,0:08:45.67,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,下一條新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:49.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,今日凌晨發生了一起大型山體滑坡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.92,0:08:54.63,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,塌方處彷彿是被人為地削去一般  存在諸多疑點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.90,0:08:55.51,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這不是我和托爾相遇的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.53,0:08:58.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,居然對我們的紀念之地做出這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:00.43,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我要找出犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.43,0:09:02.43,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,送他進去欣嫩谷  或者叫晢罕南
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.43,0:09:02.43,Kobayashi S2 - Comment,,0,0,0,,註：欣嫩谷，是耶路撒冷原本作為垃圾場和亂葬崗使用的一個谷地，希伯來聖經中提及
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.43,0:09:02.43,Kobayashi S2 - Comment,,0,0,0,,{\pos(88,61)}猶大諸王在此處以火犧牲自己孩子，後成為煉獄的代名詞。伊斯蘭教中將類似的概念稱為晢罕南。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.68,0:09:04.64,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,最後餵給阿米特吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.68,0:09:04.64,Kobayashi S2 - Comment,,0,0,0,,註：阿穆特，古埃及神話中鱷頭、獅上身、河馬下身的生物，死後審判中被認定的惡人會被它吞下，永遠不能安息。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.98,0:09:07.15,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不過能做到這種事的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.23,0:09:13.11,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,那個時間我在複習遊戲活動要用到的打call和口號
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.81,0:09:13.11,Kobayashi S2 - Name,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,868.333)\3c&H953F3E&\fad(700,0)}法夫納
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.81,0:09:13.11,Kobayashi S2 - isDragon,,0,0,0,,{\fad(700,0)\3c&H953F3E&}（其實是龍）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:15.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,露科亞昨天在國外
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.08,0:09:19.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,因為我們的魔力是連接在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.24,0:09:21.95,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她在哪裡我都能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.37,0:09:24.79,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,鯛魚燒  真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.08,0:09:25.33,Kobayashi S2 - Name,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)\pos(964,874)\3c&HED5C2A&}艾爾瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.08,0:09:25.33,Kobayashi S2 - isDragon,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)\3c&HED5C2A&}（其實是龍）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.43,0:09:31.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你突然幹什麼啊  托爾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.49,0:09:32.55,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,犯人就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.67,0:09:33.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.67,0:09:35.80,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,艾爾瑪  今天新聞報道說有座山…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:40.51,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,對了  我也很在意那個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.28,0:09:42.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,也不是艾爾瑪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.70,0:09:44.77,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我還以為是托爾做的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:45.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.86,0:09:46.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.56,0:09:49.23,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那就是說不是我們認識的龍做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:52.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,能破壞我的結界的龍很少
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.15,0:09:54.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.65,0:09:55.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.62,0:10:02.04,Kobayashi S2 - Name,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)\pos(972.8,893.4)\3c&H9C48F1&}伊露露
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.89,0:10:06.79,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.21,0:10:08.79,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,伊露露
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:14.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,很美麗的街景
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.31,0:10:16.55,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,歡笑著的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.86,0:10:21.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,在這裡就能盡情地享受破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.51,0:10:25.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是混沌之龍卻在和人類一同嬉笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.02,0:10:28.19,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我有點興趣  所以稍微觀察了一陣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.81,0:10:30.36,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是已經看膩了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.86,0:10:33.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,簡單來說  你是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:42.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.41,0:10:42.95,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是伊露露
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.39,0:10:45.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,屬於混沌勢力中最偏激的派系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.52,0:10:47.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,她很享受破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.91,0:10:49.75,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,肯定是跟著托爾過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:53.84,Kobayashi S2 - HandWrite,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H000000&\bord4\b0\pos(968.667,848.333)}自己就是跟著托爾過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.29,0:10:54.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不用說  那傢伙肯定是想毀滅這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.21,0:10:57.01,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是  托爾肯定有辦法解決的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.30,0:11:00.64,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林  伊露露只比托爾稍弱一些
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:03.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但是她們的戰鬥會把這一帶都破壞的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.51,0:11:05.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,關於這點  她也會想辦法解決的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.02,0:11:07.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你相信託爾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.82,0:11:11.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,畢竟我能做的也只有這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:13.44,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,所以我當然要相信她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:17.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不准在這個世界搞破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:21.11,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,瞎說什麼  我可是混沌勢力的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.57,0:11:24.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,做不到就揍你一頓然後送你回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.62,0:11:26.58,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要打架可是求之不得
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.04,0:11:30.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這種程度的攻擊對我可沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:39.38,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不好  目標是城市
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.18,0:11:46.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好燙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.43,0:11:49.28,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.89,0:11:51.31,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這是陷入苦戰了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:54.15,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托爾要一邊保護城市一邊戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:55.19,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,處境非常不利
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.90,0:11:58.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,艾爾瑪不去幫她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.05,0:11:59.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:04.07,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我是調和勢力  按理說跟托爾是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:06.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,雖然我展開了驅散人類的結界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.96,0:12:08.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但那只是為了避免麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.00,0:12:10.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,其他的龍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.66,0:12:11.75,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,法夫納閣下的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.92,0:12:14.08,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,估計會說「自己的屁股自己去擦」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.98,0:12:17.67,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,露科亞閣下是旁觀勢力  所以不會出手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.15,0:12:19.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,至於康納則力量不足
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:22.72,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托爾被打敗的話  我就去戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:25.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我會保護好小林以及這座城市
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.89,0:12:27.56,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那托爾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.09,0:12:34.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我嘴上說著相信託爾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.96,0:12:36.91,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但這並不能幫助到托爾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.91,0:12:38.82,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,跟無動於衷沒有區別
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.36,0:12:41.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但除此之外  我也只能…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.72,0:12:43.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,艾爾瑪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.74,0:12:48.33,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林  你要我去幫托爾是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.53,0:12:48.91,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,布丁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:51.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,等等  再怎麼說也別想用這個收買我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.70,0:12:52.58,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,泡芙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.05,0:12:53.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,咖啡凍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.33,0:12:55.23,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,巧克力蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.65,0:12:57.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,楓糖漿鬆餅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.84,0:13:00.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你想吃多少甜品都買給你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.77,0:13:16.17,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:21.48,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我打中了30發炎酸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.07,0:13:24.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,爪擊也有重擊了好幾次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:26.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你就說一句「好痛」？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.16,0:13:28.03,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這可難辦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.58,0:13:30.20,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,想不到該怎麼殺死你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.54,0:13:31.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.41,0:13:34.91,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,全力攻擊的話會毀壞城市
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.33,0:13:37.58,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但不這樣做的話  就無法打倒你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:41.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,對於你的攻擊  我也快忍無可忍了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.23,0:13:44.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但又必須保護城市
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:47.93,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我快炸裂了  不如乾脆毀滅一切
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.10,0:13:50.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,還在逞強
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.81,0:13:52.25,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托爾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.10,0:13:55.10,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,艾爾瑪展開屏障了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.27,0:13:57.65,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我不過是和小林做了份交易
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.94,0:14:01.98,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那又怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.61,0:14:06.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,和人類打成一片  讓我感到噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.03,0:14:08.66,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,接下來我要動真格的了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.95,0:14:11.41,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,以我真正的形態毀滅這整個世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.18,0:14:35.23,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,差點沒控制住自己
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:38.27,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,雖然受到的傷害並沒那麼嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:42.11,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但我卻差點忘記自己要保護這座城市
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.15,0:14:47.49,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,甚至一度覺得除了小林之外的人小林以外的人死了也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.31,0:14:50.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這樣的話就不能再待在這個世界了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:14:57.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,小林  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:11.68,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:15.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.14,0:15:20.98,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,無論多艱難我都能努力下去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.02,0:15:23.90,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,只要為了能留在小林身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.41,0:15:26.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,任何艱難險阻都攔不住我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:38.29,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那個人類
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.00,0:15:41.96,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,說服了艾爾瑪出手幫助托爾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.92,0:15:46.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我一直被教導說人類是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.24,0:15:46.88,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,然而
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.68,0:15:49.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我想了解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.72,0:15:52.22,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那個人類
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.47,0:16:02.52,Kobayashi S2 - Name,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,0)\3c&HD25090&\pos(965.6,865.8)}露科亞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.47,0:16:02.52,Kobayashi S2 - isDragon,,0,0,0,,{\3c&HD25090&\fad(600,0)}（其實是龍）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.47,0:15:59.02,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,「是我」？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.70,0:16:00.44,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,你到底是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:03.97,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,感冒？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.44,0:16:06.36,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,電車？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.78,0:16:07.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,背包？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:14.78,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,賠償  今天之內  200萬？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.82,0:16:22.70,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那是有點棘手哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.80,0:16:37.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,光是打開傳送門就累死個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.91,0:16:41.98,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,真虧托爾能把這麼費勁的事情做得易如反掌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.53,0:16:44.98,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,趕末班車嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:48.03,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,要不讓托爾來接我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.63,0:16:50.19,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.71,0:16:51.99,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,名為小林的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.15,0:16:55.07,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,為什麼你能和龍生活在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.52,0:16:57.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我並沒有做過什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.85,0:17:00.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,而是托爾主動迎合我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.87,0:17:02.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你不恐懼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.71,0:17:03.58,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,感到恐懼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:07.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,畢竟這麼可愛  有什麼怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:08.13,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.24,0:17:11.42,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你對她發情了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.55,0:17:15.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你迷上了化身成人類形態的托爾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.41,0:17:16.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,所以才不怕她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.28,0:17:20.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不是不是  瞎說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.81,0:17:21.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,強烈地否定了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.29,0:17:22.95,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.95,0:17:23.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我都說不是了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.48,0:17:25.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.90,0:17:31.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這什麼鬼  好誇張
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.26,0:17:32.94,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.45,0:17:37.03,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你終究不過是個人類  違抗不了欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.66,0:17:41.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,來吧  將你那下流的男人本性暴露無遺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.82,0:17:43.16,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,很想沉溺在這溫柔鄉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.46,0:17:45.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,僅限此刻我允許你對我發洩慾望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.14,0:17:46.62,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.05,0:17:48.29,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,來吧  來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.79,0:17:50.55,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我可是女的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.34,0:17:50.34,Kobayashi S2 - UP,,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:17:52.76,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.09,0:17:57.84,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,每天我見到那兩坨巨大的脂肪塊就又氣又恨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.00,0:18:00.35,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,趕不上末班車了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.81,0:18:01.26,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.77,0:18:06.06,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,車門關閉  請勿靠近車門
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.31,0:18:18.32,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.67,0:18:20.12,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,還沒鬧夠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:24.83,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我無法認同你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:28.58,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,龍與人類不可能共存
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.57,0:18:32.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,兩者共處就會因各自差異而感到痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.23,0:18:35.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,一直痛苦下去  乃至將憎恨上升至種族
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.97,0:18:40.01,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,尊敬轉化成嫉妒  早晚產生裂痕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.58,0:18:43.52,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,托爾對你的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.12,0:18:45.56,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不過是稀奇感罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.19,0:18:48.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,等她對你失去興趣  終有一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.77,0:18:51.71,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,別睡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:55.57,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,沒事  聽著呢聽著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.67,0:18:56.43,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,騙人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.11,0:18:59.86,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,總之就是什麼種族差異之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.46,0:19:02.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不認可我對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:06.29,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那你還要說服我這種人幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.70,0:19:08.00,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我要你糾正自己的認知
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:14.80,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那麼就讓我借用你剛才的話來說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.31,0:19:17.66,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我們因各自差異而感到快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.06,0:19:20.05,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,一直快樂下去  乃至將喜愛上升至種族
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:24.37,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,尊敬轉化成信賴  早晚產生牽絆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.58,0:19:28.85,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我從和托爾的生活裡感受到的就是這些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.39,0:19:30.90,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你這不過是詭辯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.27,0:19:32.54,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,實際上很可能釀成悲劇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.92,0:19:35.11,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你這不過是在用漂亮的話語敷衍而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.62,0:19:37.40,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.90,0:19:41.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我們會爭吵  也產生過裂痕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.78,0:19:46.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但對此視而不見  產生負面情緒也無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.00,0:19:49.21,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,即便不能正確理解對方的情感
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.56,0:19:51.25,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,但也會用自己的方式嘗試配合彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.45,0:19:52.63,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,總能湊合著生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.21,0:19:54.75,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,我就是這種人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.97,0:19:56.92,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這就是人類的思維方式嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:20:00.30,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,不  是小林我個人的思維方式
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.46,0:20:06.11,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你沒有把龍的思維方式和伊露露的思維方式區分開嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.07,0:20:09.39,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,沒必要區分  都是相同的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.14,0:20:10.81,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.66,0:20:15.61,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,那麼決定「龍的思維方式」的龍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.09,0:20:18.11,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,並不是伊露露這條龍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.93,0:20:39.46,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你說得再天花亂墜  也不過是個人類
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.14,0:20:42.05,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,你身為女人  所以才不能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.92,0:20:54.69,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,伊露露是離開了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.38,0:21:05.24,Kobayashi S2 - TEXT,,0,0,0,,這是什麼
